OL,3,CWhat the Romans left for us: Project
OL,4,Cto combat ancient mining legacy
OL,6,FRachel Bullock has been finding out
OL,7,Fhow an 800 metre long structure in the
OL,8,FRiver Tyne could benefit businesses
OL,9,Fand wildlife
OL,11,FA groundbreaking project to deal with
OL,12,Fthe legacy of mining dating back to
OL,13,Fthe Romans could be set to go ahead.
OL,15,FThe contamination in the River Tyne
OL,16,Fmay have been there for centuries, but
OL,17,Fit remains a problem for modern
OL,18,Findustry.
