OL,3,CWhat the Romans left for us: Project
OL,4,Cto combat ancient mining legacy
OL,6,FMetals that Roman miners dumped into
OL,7,Fthe river remain buried deep within
OL,8,Fits sediment. Severe storms can cause
OL,9,Fit to shift, causing serious issues.
OL,11,FThe harmful material cannot be fully
OL,12,Fdredged and can drift downstream to
OL,13,Fhinder the operation of businesses
OL,14,Falong the river.
OL,16,FA new project will see an 800 metre
OL,17,Flong structure put in the water to
OL,18,Fprevent the legacy metals from flowing
OL,19,Fdownstream.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
