OL,3,CWhat the Romans left for us: Project
OL,4,Cto combat ancient mining legacy
OL,6,FIt has been specially designed for the
OL,7,FRiver Tyne and its unique legacy
OL,8,Fcontamination.
OL,10,FResembling a giant curve, it will
OL,11,Fintercept sediment east of Newcastle
OL,12,Fcity centre, at Bill Point. It will be
OL,13,Fmade up of rocks close to the
OL,14,Friverbank.
OL,16,FThe contaminated sediment will then be
OL,17,Flifted and safely removed, rather than
OL,18,Fdumped out at sea.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
