OL,3,CWhat the Romans left for us: Project
OL,4,Cto combat ancient mining legacy
OL,6,FPlanning permission is still being
OL,7,Fsought but if passed, construction
OL,8,Fshould begin in early 2026.
OL,10,FAndrew Rollo, an advisor from
OL,11,FNewcastle City Council, said:
OL,12,F"Businesses on the Tyne support up to
OL,13,F4,000 jobs so the project is really
OL,14,Fkey to protect that and ensure those
OL,15,Fbusinesses can operate effectively. We
OL,16,Fbelieve it's the first of its kind in
OL,17,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
