OL,3,CWhat the Romans left for us: Project
OL,4,Cto combat ancient mining legacy
OL,6,F"It will mimic the rock foreshore so
OL,7,Fin terms of visual impact it will be
OL,8,Fquite low. It's going to be about 800
OL,9,Fmetres in length and at its widest
OL,10,Fwill be 100 metres in width."
OL,12,FIt is hoped the structure could also
OL,13,Fbenefit wildlife in the area, and on
OL,14,Fthe coast.
